# ActivityBar
Simple to use Perl module for displaying an animated activity bar in the terminal.

Author: Jeremy Melanson <zish@systemhalted.com>
Last updated: 2015-09-23

Source-code, documentation and revision Git repository:
  https://github.com/zish/

  $ git clone https://github.com/zish/perl-ActivityBar.git

